race.comment: Tricky race to kick off the card with many of these facing the starter for the first time. Of the raced brigade ENTERPRISE KHAN (1) hit the frame on debut when well in the betting before being tipped out for further time to mature. Revved up for this with two recent trials and has race experience over a lot of these. Can return a winner. TENGUN JESSIE (7) is at the races for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and is sure to be well-educated out of the Anderson barn. Keep very safe. HELLO PUNTERS (2) has placed over this sprint journey and gets some weight relief with the 1.5kg claim. In the mix. REEVACITY (6) placed in a recent Sunny Coast trial and may make her presence felt on debut. HIT THE KEY (4) best of the rest.
